<font style="font-family: Verdana, arial; font-size: 10pt" color="Navy"><h3>Definitions</h3></font>
<font style="font-family: Verdana, arial; font-size: 8pt" color="Black">
The user is any person using the Internet network to consult information on the site www.alloweb.com.
The member is any individual or legal entity publishing information on the site www.alloweb.com.
The company MICRO-ASSISTANCE is both the administrator and the publisher of the site.
</font>
<font style="font-family: Verdana, arial; font-size: 10pt" color="Navy"><h3>Responsability of the members</h3></font>
<font style="font-family: Verdana, arial; font-size: 8pt" color="Black">
Each member undertakes to :
1. publish only commercially correct information
2. correct without delay all mistakes communicated by the administrator of the site or any user
3. notify immediately all changements concerning the services or the manufactured and represented goods. 
Any shortcoming of this duty will be corrected by the administrator of the site without previous notice or formal request.
</font>
<font style="font-family: Verdana, arial; font-size: 10pt" color="Navy"><h3>User's right</h3></font>
<font style="font-family: Verdana, arial; font-size: 8pt" color="Black">
Each user detecting mystakes in the information published by members has to inform either the responsible member, in writing, or by e-mail, or the administrator of the site by e-mail.
</font>
<font style="font-family: Verdana, arial; font-size: 10pt" color="Navy"><h3>Confidentiality of the information sent by e-mail</h3></font>
<font style="font-family: Verdana, arial; font-size: 8pt" color="Black">
All information sent by e-mail is confidential and can not in any case be publicized to a third party without written authorization.
</font>
<font style="font-family: Verdana, arial; font-size: 10pt" color="Navy"><h3>Royalties</h3></font>
<font style="font-family: Verdana, arial; font-size: 8pt" color="Black">
The site www.alloweb.com is protected by the laws governing the royalties. Any violation of these laws will automatically lead to legal proceedings.
Each member undertakes to publish only personal information or with the written authorization of the owner. 
This is also applicable to texts, commercial or technical descriptions, drawings, logos and photos.
Reproduction be it in full or partial of members' information without the written permission of the member is prohibited.
The database is the exclusive property of the administrator of the site and can not in any case be copied or reproduced.
</font>
<font style="font-family: Verdana, arial; font-size: 10pt" color="Navy"><h3>Terms, clauses and conditions</h3></font>
<font style="font-family: Verdana, arial; font-size: 8pt" color="Black">
The use of this site implies the acceptance of the characteristics of the site and the terms, clauses and conditions specified hereunder.
The objective of the site is to allow the user to search, consult and process data on a database made up of information available to the public, concerning names of persons, addresses and contact details, fields of activity and the products of companies and individuals working on the Belgian market.
Not included, however, in the database is any information related to companies or individuals who have requested being excluded.  
The publisher of the site, ALLOWEB and the suppliers of data are explicitly excluded from all responsability for damages resulting from the inaccuracy of information extracted from the public domain and which is used on the site.   
The user must demonstrate the existence of any serious error or grievance which is the direct cause of any damages incurred.

In the event that the responsability of the publisher and/or Alloweb is established, this can only extend as far as reimbursement of the membership fee.
</font>
<font style="font-family: Verdana, arial; font-size: 10pt" color="Navy"><h3>Protection of privacy</h3></font>
