This site has been the subject of a declaration made to the Commission for the Protection of Privacy n° 001920006.
<br>File Master: Micro-Assistance 6, Rue Infante Isabelle 7180 Seneffe.<br>
Any person, proving his identity, has the right of access to the data concerning him/her on the site and to obtain a correction (without cost) of all the data which are of a personal character and which are incorrect.
Similarly, any person, proving his identity, may request that the data concerning them are removed. 

In order to ensure that this request comes from the person concerned, it should be sent by recorded delivery with acknowledgement of receipt to the File Master together with a copy of proof of identity. 
Requests from companies must, in addition, be accompanied by a mandate proving that the individual making this request has power of representation.

The File Master undertakes to destroy or return any data communicated on the occasion of these requests.

The user of the site is held responsible for abiding by the observation of the requirements of the law of 8 December 1992 regarding the Protection of Privacy in the processing of data of personal character. 
